OL,3,CFormer PwC employee settles
OL,4,Cdiscrimination claim
OL,6,FA former employee of a "Big 4"
OL,7,Faccounting company in Belfast has
OL,8,Fsettled a discrimination case for
OL,9,F#150,000.
OL,11,FA woman who had worked for
OL,12,FPricewaterhouseCoopers Services Ltd
OL,13,F(PwC) for more than 40 years has
OL,14,Fsettled her case of age and disability
OL,15,Fdiscrimination against the company,
OL,16,Fsupported by the Equality Commission
OL,17,Ffor Northern Ireland.
