OL,3,CFormer PwC employee settles
OL,4,Cdiscrimination claim
OL,6,FThe woman, who worked as an executive
OL,7,Fsupport assistant, said that a senior
OL,8,Fcolleague unexpectedly raised concerns
OL,9,Fabout her knowledge of new technology.
OL,11,FIn addition, she says she was asked if
OL,12,Ftraining was something she was
OL,13,Finterested in at her age.
OL,15,FThe woman also reported being told
OL,16,Fthat, because of her length of
OL,17,Fservice, she was just working towards
OL,18,Fher pension, and that she looked tired
OL,19,Fand should consider taking time off
OL,20,Ffor caring responsibilities.
