OL,3,CFormer PwC employee settles
OL,4,Cdiscrimination claim
OL,6,FThe woman then submitted a formal
OL,7,Fgrievance feeling "stunned and upset"
OL,8,Fby what she believed were "unfair and
OL,9,Fdiscriminatory remarks".
OL,11,FShe claimed this then led to
OL,12,Funjustified performance criticisms by
OL,13,Fsenior colleagues, despite having
OL,14,Freceived consistently strong
OL,15,Fperformance reviews over many years.
OL,17,FThe internal grievance investigation
OL,18,Fconcluded that she had experienced
OL,19,Fharassment but found that it did not
OL,20,Famount to unlawful discrimination.
