OL,4,Cdiscrimination claim
OL,6,FThe woman was later told that her
OL,7,Fappeal against this decision was
OL,8,Funsuccessful.
OL,10,FAs part of the settlement she ended
OL,11,Fher employment with PwC.
OL,13,FThe woman, who has remained anonymous,
OL,14,Fsaid she dedicated her working life to
OL,15,FPwC and was "heartbroken".
OL,17,F"I never imagined this is how my
OL,18,Fcareer would end after such loyal
OL,19,Fservice," she said.
