OL,6,F"It has been an extremely distressing
OL,7,Fand stressful experience.
OL,9,F"I felt compelled to bring this case,
OL,10,Fnot only to seek justice for myself,
OL,11,Fbut to act as a voice for others who
OL,12,Fmay suffer in silence."
OL,14,FGeraldine McGahey, chief commissioner,
OL,15,FEquality Commission for Northern
OL,16,FIreland, said: "This long-serving
OL,17,Femployee believes her age and caring
OL,18,Fresponsibilities became an issue for
OL,19,Fher employer, leading to this
OL,20,Fsituation.
