OL,6,F"In Northern Ireland, it is unlawful
OL,7,Fto discriminate against employees
OL,8,Fbecause of their age. Older workers
OL,9,Fbring valuable experience, skills and
OL,10,Finsight to the workforce.
OL,12,F"The commission provides advice and
OL,13,Fguidance to help employers comply with
OL,14,Four equality laws. All employees,
OL,15,Fregardless of their age, deserve to be
OL,16,Ftreated with dignity and respect in
OL,17,Fthe workplace."
