OL,3,CFormer PwC employee settles
OL,4,Cdiscrimination claim
OL,6,FIn settling the case, PwC expressed
OL,7,Fregret for the upset and distress
OL,8,Fexperienced by their former employee
OL,9,Fand provided a reference, as well as
OL,10,Freaffirming its strong commitment to
OL,11,Fequality of opportunity in employment.
OL,13,FThe case was settled without admission
OL,14,Fof liability.
OL,16,FIn a statement PwC UK said it is "very
OL,17,Fsorry for the experience this employee
OL,18,Fhad towards the end of what was a
OL,19,Fsuccessful career".
